1. Write a Java program that takes an integer (1â€“7) and prints the corresponding day name (e.g., 1 â†’ Monday)

public class DayOfWeek
 {
    public static void main(String[] args) {
      
             int num = 1();

        switch (day) 
{
            case 1:
                   System.out.println("Sunday"); 
                    break;
            case 2:
                   System.out.println("Monday");
                    break;
            case 3: 
                   System.out.println("Tuesday");
                    break;
